{"id": "6863067eb0a2c7499425c6c189b2c88bac55ca754285a6ab1ef37b75b4cfad4d", "item_id": "935b81ca87:0", "text": "参见"}
{"id": "07a8ec1c9566d237d6cfd01372f6a08e4a4e32a76296552cbdb1fd636f38d800", "item_id": "935b81ca87:1", "text": "Subdivision Surfaces（细分曲面）"}
{"id": "18b4573c14992c774fb9977921c55d5d2500a00208765fca79aee1e0ff699d99", "item_id": "935b81ca87:2", "text": "了解有关 subdivision surfaces（细分曲面）的更多信息。"}
{"id": "641174b7ee170c5e60da3067ddba10e6668ef6a07dd029e1b812174ad6eb2bda", "item_id": "935b81ca87:3", "text": "tessellation（曲面细分）较差的非细分曲面在渲染时可能会出现瑕疵，例如暗边和轮廓线。建议渲染平滑细分来避免这种瑕疵。也可以使用未定义法线的多边形再进行细分，RenderMan 会为你计算法线。"}
{"id": "60a35741887f7373535a77bb70d987e17002fec25efa1006c49d1314beef751f", "item_id": "935b81ca87:4", "text": "若要将多边形渲染为 subdivision surface（细分曲面），请将 RenderMan 选项卡添加到 OBJ 节点。在 Geometry > SubdivisionMesh 展开项中启用 \"Render Polygons As Subdivision\" 参数。还需要将 Style 参数设为 Catmull-Clark、Bilinear 或 Loop。"}
{"id": "d439ce3cf85aaeaae4c4e0188217c329a7525d44196d87c1ade3af9a05cd9f94", "item_id": "935b81ca87:5", "text": "若要匹配来自 Maya 的几何体（这是常见需求，也是默认设置），你会看到："}
{"id": "b0dfa3cd270ec8e713c712a3a64a6fa430de12a6271d058c9457a2e6d6431c1f", "item_id": "935b81ca87:6", "text": "Catmull-Clark"}
{"id": "7f29f649dd660c9e55e092759631ba6c26205af1e9faa9369e90ce460450432a", "item_id": "935b81ca87:7", "text": "Interpolation（插值）：Sharp Creases and Corners（锐利折痕和角点）"}
{"id": "f865920b80570ab2aaeeecfc03047c2565aaabadf27660244d101ce3f4cb40b4", "item_id": "935b81ca87:8", "text": "Facevarying Boundary（Facevarying 边界）：New Style, internal only（新样式，仅内部）"}
{"id": "90011d7903b41cf2b669ccede89dab4ba736fad94fe2a97824db1d513c567176", "item_id": "935b81ca87:9", "text": "有关这些设置的详细信息和插图，可在 RenderMan 的以下页面中找到："}
{"id": "07a8ec1c9566d237d6cfd01372f6a08e4a4e32a76296552cbdb1fd636f38d800", "item_id": "935b81ca87:10", "text": "Subdivision Surfaces（细分曲面）"}
{"id": "faa1d50fa43eaf810e2c97546e2b39203222948bcceacbf61d09c1d79114c4db", "item_id": "935b81ca87:11", "text": "此图像使用"}
{"id": "f0a9da745007933c4e95f751f7e9b60c17dccad290fc197841acefc1c93cc398", "item_id": "935b81ca87:12", "text": "PxrVisualizer"}
{"id": "d16244f6a2f87dab811d9b5ecbbd3926034f54e3ac71a4739d9ad27a9c494ffb", "item_id": "935b81ca87:13", "text": "积分器在 Houdini 中渲染。"}
